name: A is For Apple Alphabet Risograph Print
description:
Bright and jolly A is for Apple poster in red.

This vibrant alphabet print would be perfect for a nursery or bedroom wall. Printed on 100% recycled 300 gsm white card with eco-friendly soya inks, this would make a lovely Christening, birthday or Christmas gift.

Risograph printing is one of the most eco-friendly print processes and gives a lovely texture to the print, much like a screen print, each one is individual and has variations within the surface.

Posted in a cellophane bag and board-backed envelope to protect from damage.

made from:
100% recyled card printed with with soya ink.

dimensions:
A4 - 21cm x 29 cm

description:

Machine washable up to 40 degrees, iron on reverse. Tumble drying is not recommended.

name: Penguin Organic Cotton Bib
description:

All my designs start off as scribbles in my sketchbook, I aim to make each one original, full of personality and gender-neutral. This smart young character was inspired by baby emperor penguins' cute little faces!

Manufactured using renewable green energy from wind and solar power and hand printed with love using no harmful chemicals, these bibs won't irritate sensitive skin.

100% organic natural coloured cotton, printed with solvent-free print paste and heat set to prevent fading.
